# _sys/txc-continuation scope 0 — continuation poll / deferred response.
#
# Reached only via the detectTenantBody short-circuit: a request
# carrying `?txc.continuation=<rcid>` (mapped to _txc.continuation by
# the web inlet) is NOT hostname-routed — boot/0's detect-tenant sets
# _txc.goto = "txc-continuation/0", jumping here pinned to _sys.
#
# txco://continuation-result reads the run by the opaque rcid (a
# capability — possession is authorization) and returns an envelope for
# the normal web response path: the stored result page once complete
# (or the JSON status doc with ?format=json), 202 + Retry-After while
# running, 502 on failure, 404 if unknown. Because this flows through
# the normal pipeline the poll appears in the trace list — unlike the
# old bus-bypassing dedicated GET it replaces.
EXEC "txco://continuation-result"
